title: A question and a favour
body:
Hey everyone, does anyone know where I can get a copy of Entertainment Weekly over here in Scotland? 

If I can’t get a hold of one over here, could someone maybe pick me up a copy and ship it over please? (I’ll PayPal you the money asap or send over a couple of these Infinity War posters if you like - not sure if I still have the Thanos one but I have loads of the others - see below).

title: Halloween Time & Place - DISNEY Reporter
body:
Halloween Time & Place – DISNEY Reporter

Welcome to this week’s edition of DISNEYReporter. This week, there is a lot going on around the Disneyland Resort. Things start off with the announcement of changes coming to two of the Disneyland Resort hotel restaurants. Also at Disneyland, Halloween has arrived. It is bigger and better than ever before! Finally, Disneyland is holding auditions for Mickey’s Soundsational Parade. Over at Hong…
